Data.Function_Help:
Splits If/Else single lines to If/Else - Begin constructs.
The function accepts a parameter controlling the If/Else or Begin/End block constructs.
Valid sParameters, See: EnumList;

Data.ParameterHelp:
Valid values;
eSplitBySpaceAndSemicolon - Split line with space and semicolon
eSplitBySemicolon - Split line with semicolon
eSplitToBeginEndBlock - Use a Begin/End block }
